# Academic ERP UI: Production-Readiness Implementation Plan

**Goal:** Convert existing 8 React screens from "feature-complete" to "production-ready"  
**Date:** February 10, 2026  
**Approach:** Systematic enhancement without changing visual design  

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **NO NEW UI SCREENS REQUIRED**
> All 8 Phase-1 screens are already implemented. This plan focuses ONLY on:
> - UI behavior resilience (empty/error/loading states)
> - User feedback (toast notifications)
> - Functionality completion (wire up existing buttons)
> - Accessibility (WCAG AA compliance)
> - Code quality (reusable components, remove duplication)

> [!WARNING]
> **ESTIMATED TIME: 40-50 hours**
> This is a substantial refactoring effort. Breaking it into 6 phases for incremental delivery.

