## Phase 3: Toast Notification System

**Goal:** Provide user feedback for all actions

### Implementation Steps

#### 3.1 Install react-hot-toast
```bash
npm install react-hot-toast
```

#### 3.2 Configure Toast Provider
- [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/App.tsx)
