  - Add `<Toaster />` component at root
  - Configure position, duration, styling

#### 3.3 Create Toast Utility
- [NEW] [utils/toast.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20new%20updae%202.0/frontend/src/utils/toast.ts)
