## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Breaking existing functionality | HIGH | Test thoroughly after each phase |
| Bundle size increase | MEDIUM | Code-split reusable components, monitor bundle |
| Accessibility regressions | MEDIUM | Run automated tests, manual keyboard testing |
| API endpoints not ready | HIGH | Mock data for missing endpoints, graceful degradation |
| Time underestimation | MEDIUM | Prioritize Phases 2-4, defer Phase 6 if needed |

